  "title": "WAREHOUSE ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong></p><ul><li>Loading and unloading cargoes from and to the containers</li><li>General warehousing and housekeeping duties</li><li>Responsible to complete the job process from Inbound to Outbound</li><li>Ensure that the administration work that goes along with the processes are conducted in a proper manner</li><li>Ensure proper records and for the stock/cargo kept in the warehouse</li><li>Working together with Warehouse Coordinator to run the day to day operations</li><li>Ad hoc work as and when may be assigned</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Be proactive towards clients and staff</li><li>Possess high integrity and strong commitment</li><li>A good team player and yet able to work independently</li></ul>",
